{"tid":892785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國監控升級！架設「步態識別」 看走路方式就能找到你","createTime":"2018-11-07T06:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T10:37:40.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7808288781354550ffdcbb1369055ba133c30b","tid":892785,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQdVE6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQdVE6X.png&h=ea9a43f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KfTKysd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKfTKysd.png&h=d5737582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國政府近日安裝了「步態識別」（gait recognition）系統，用來監視人民，號稱光從人們的身形、走路姿勢就可以辨別身分，即使把臉遮住也沒用。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，繼人臉辨識系統後，中國北京銀河水滴科技公司研發出「步態識別」系統，目前架設在北京、上海的街道上，銀河水滴的執行長黃永禎說，這個系統最大的特點是可以遠距離運作，有別於他生物辨識技術，距離50公尺遠就開始辨析人物，就算是背影、人臉被遮住、光線昏暗，都不會影響系統判斷。<br />\n<br />\n黃永禎進一步說明，就算人們在系統前故意走路外八或彎腰駝背掩飾也沒用，因為這套系統是運用全身所有特徵下去辨別分析。<br />\n<br />\n雖然說步態識別系統並非新技術，但目前除了中國，尚未聽聞有國家將它運用在監控人民，美國《華爾街日報》曾撰文批評中國政府運用監視系統控制民眾，報導指出，美國運用這種技術是為了辨別、找出嫌疑犯，中國卻拿來用在監控人民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2604316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2604316&d=8pkJm4AEPJNnEtdN9MQM%2BQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=d7df1a18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2604316&h=28b1d74d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2604316</a>"},{"pid":"bd84137c3f005ef2011eb50b59d541973c0efb66","tid":892785,"uid":93986,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VExfE8f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVExfE8f.png&h=3691b236&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38e9ccbeccebc98256c2e8f6666dfdb13a18c6e9","tid":892785,"uid":97526,"